Interface MultiFilingService

  • All Known Subinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface MultiFilingService
    MultiFiling Service interface.

    See the CMIS 1.0 and CMIS 1.1 specifications for details on the operations, parameters, exceptions and the domain model.

        Adds an existing fileable non-folder object to a folder.
        Parameters:
        repositoryId - the identifier for the repository
        objectId - the object to add
        folderId - the folder
        allVersions - a flag that indicates if all versions of a document should be added to the folder or just this single version
        extension - extension data
